column16: Jeff Keppinger grounds out softly to first baseman Micah Hoffpauir.
Hunter Pence singles on a ground ball to left fielder Alfonso Soriano.
Geoff Blum flies out to left fielder Alfonso Soriano.
Matt Kata flies out to center fielder Kosuke Fukudome.
Hunter Pence grounds into double play, shortstop Andres Blanco to first baseman Micah Hoffpauir.    Carlos Lee out at 2nd.
Geoff Blum pops out to catcher Koyie Hill in foul territory.
Carlos Lee reaches on fielding error by third baseman Jeff Baker.
